trans-unit.source: Represents the name of a queue associated with an event on a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance" />.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta il nome di una coda associato a un evento in una classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance" />.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Questa classe non può essere ereditata.

trans-unit.source: This class can be associated with a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> or any other queues used by the Workflow Foundation (WF).
trans-unit.target: Questa classe può essere associata a una coda <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> o a qualsiasi altra utilizzata da Workflow Foundation (WF).
